-- United Technologies Cancels Furlough for 2,000 for This Week
-- B y   K a t h l e e n   M i l l e r
-- 2013-10-06T15:30:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-06/united-technologies-cancels-furlough-for-2-000-for-this-week.html
United Technologies Corp. (UTX) , a military
supplier, has canceled furloughs for 2,000 employees after the
Pentagon said it would send many civilian employees back to work
during the federal shutdown.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kathleen Miller in Washington at 
